Class Village

  • java.lang.Object
    • ue3.Village

  • public class Village
extends java.lang.Object
    The class Village describes a Village with name, population, amount of houses and a mayor. - It has to have a name
    Author:
    Paul Jureschek, Michael Kinzkofer
